forohfor.scryfall.api

Class CardReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • forohfor.scryfall.api.CardReference

  • public class CardReference
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a reference to a single printing of a card. Used for cards with multiple parts to refer to the pages of the other parts.
    Author:
    ForOhForError
